PrecisSetting apart for the PETER BALLANTYNE CREE NATION BAND of some 128 hectares of land situated near the City of Prince Albert, Saskatchewan, together with mines and minerals, including those within the road allowance, as a reserve named Kistapinan Indian Reserve No. 211.
